03:45.086 --> 03:47.641
I'’ve had gentlemen
walk into my shop and boast,

03:47.675 --> 03:50.264
"Oh, I don'’t care about
what I wear."

03:50.299 --> 03:54.958
And assuming that'’s true,
doesn'’t that say something, too?

04:10.457 --> 04:12.252
So, who is your customer?

04:12.286 --> 04:14.184
