04:18.361 --> 04:23.297
A man walks through your door,
what about him can you observe?

04:23.332 --> 04:24.954
-[bell jingles]
-Good morning.

04:24.988 --> 04:26.438
Is he timid,

04:26.473 --> 04:29.648
hunched over
like a midday clock?

04:29.683 --> 04:32.962
