with confidence,

04:32.996 --> 04:35.482
spine at six and twelve?

04:36.828 --> 04:40.625
Is this a man
of springtime pastel,

04:40.659 --> 04:43.317
clamoring to be noticed?

04:43.352 --> 04:47.770
Or is this a man
of gray and brown,

04:47.804 --> 04:52.015
blending into the hurried crowd?

04:52.050 --> 04:55.536
Is this a man comfortable
in his station?

04:56.986 --> 04:58.436
[bell jingles]

04:58.470 --> 05:01.162
Or does he pine
for grander things?

05:04.234 --> 05:07.203
And who would this man
like to be?

05:12.657 --> 05:14.383
And who is he underneath?

05:20.492 --> 05:22.701
[jingles]

05:52.904 --> 05:54.423
Take your measure...

05:57.633 --> 06:01.257
...and when you understand
who he is...

06:01.291 --> 06:03.466
[jingles]

06:06.469 --> 06:08.022
